<L>__{interior sullivan house study night 1969}
<C>__{frank}
<P>__{(into radio mic)}
<D>__{johnny? johnny? you there? c'mon, chief, answer me...}
<A>__{nothing but static. frank jiggles the frequency dial.}
<C>__{frank }
<D>__{chief?}
<P>__{(louder)}
<D>__{chief, are you there?}
<A>__{silence. and then a voice...}
<C>__{johnny }
<D>__{i'm right here, daddy.}
<A>__{frank turns. johnny, sleepy faced, wrapped in his blankie, stands just outside the room he looks a little scared.}
<C>__{frank}
<D>__{it's okay, chief.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{c'mere.}
<A>__{johnny shuffles over, frank lifts him up on his knee brushes the hair out of his face...and gets an idea.}
